query:
/*+  */ select b1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 10 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'ell',
'judaism')
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('halacha',
'minhag',
'organic-chemistry',
'physical-chemistry')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND acc.website_url ilike '%code%'
inner join badge AS b1
on s.site_id = b1.site_id AND b1.user_id = u1.id group by b1.name order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
